CONJUNCTION:


G |- A set           G |- B set
--------------------------------- &-form
G |- A & B set


G |- A & B set       G |- a : A       G |- b : B
-------------------------------------------------- &-intro
G |- (a , b) : A & B


G |- p : A & B           G, x : A, y : B |- c : C
-------------------------------------------------- &-elim
G |- split p c : C


G |- (a , b) : A & B     G, x : A, y : B |- c : C
-------------------------------------------------- &-comp
G |- split (a , b) c = c[x\a,y\b] : C

